{"tid":1516433,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黑警可能根本就最唔想呢單野完結 個個月都出三糧","createTime":"2019-08-29T14:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T04:59:17.000Z","uid":36134,"like":314,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"79d1380246fd719dead859da32dd07a183501792","tid":1516433,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"1至5又唔洗做 咇都唔洗行<br />\n六日又stand by 唔會全部出動<br />\n又越黎越多特權<br />\n仲特登派多d臥底扔汽油瓶<br />\n仲要粒粒都扔唔中 製造沖突升級 <br />\n繼續製造矛盾<br />\n捉住d義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又拉晒去虐打中心<br />\n玩恐懼鬥室<br />\n越亂越有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似中共地方官維穩一樣道理姐<br />\n你唔亂 邊得黎咁多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">維穩費</span></span><br />\n越亂越發達"},{"pid":"6695b354a320f482b2a681e66aa32072ec3e250c","tid":1516433,"uid":36134,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"黑警可能係最唔想呢場運動完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7c893fb3cd665e5aa77f0362d288c63a40d57f","tid":1516433,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f0120cf9890ffa5084013c41ff48e812fd39a0","tid":1516433,"uid":171313,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"做幾個月夠比首期<br />\n黑警最開心"},{"pid":"8e61a3d5bc0e6960724551bac9e49c54a3de6e8e","tid":1516433,"uid":36134,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"94f0120cf9890ffa5084013c41ff48e812fd39a0","tid":1516433,"uid":171313,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"做幾個月夠比首期<br />\n黑警最開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"大部分黑警根本就係standby <br />\n唔洗出動"},{"pid":"ffd950ddebd40da6bdbf848e5392a202990d18d8","tid":1516433,"uid":236646,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"c